author: eglynn
msg: Added a no-op PolicyInterceptorProvider so as to prevent the policy enforcement logic making it impossible to assert the HTTPClientPolicy upfront before the HTTPConduit becomes invoved (e.g. via a WSPolicyFeature applied to the <jawx:client> bean).

msg: Fixed issue with groovy where if Script was cached the context was ignored; note that I could not find a thread safe way to run a parsed script, so this versio only caches the script text; need to find a way to parse just the script and run from the cache; the performance in this isn't terrible, but isn't good either
